{"tid":1817961,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新增十宗發燒或肺炎病徵病人病發前都無到過武漢濕街市","createTime":"2020-01-09T13:24:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T14:17:27.000Z","uid":173631,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"319ef259f11172e8b0f04408341f749e2ed010d6","tid":1817961,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:24:01.000Z","msg":"過多二日多過武漢？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501931-20200109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501931-20200109.htm&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF07TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=a8061a45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1501931-20200109.htm&h=3a44661e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1501931-20200109.htm</a><br />\n新增十宗發燒或肺炎病徵病人病發前都無到過武漢濕街市<br />\n2020-01-09 HKT 21:03<br />\n 分享工具  facebook  twitter<br />\n醫管局表示，截至中午12時，公立醫院於過去24小時共接收10名曾於過去14天到訪過武漢，並出現發燒、呼吸道感染或肺炎徵狀的病人，涉及5男5女，年齡由11個月大至66歲，全部於病發前沒有到過武漢的濕街市。累計數字48宗，有25人已經出院，所有留院病人情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n另外，醫管局傳染病及緊急應變中央委員會再度召開特別會議，討論武漢嚴重新型傳染性病原體呼吸系統病組群個案的最新情況。醫管局重申個人保護裝備儲備，例如外科手術口罩及N95口罩等，可足夠使用3個月，有關使用量是以2009年豬流感爆發時的最高使用量作參考。醫管局並就個人保護裝備及被服供應問題，設立熱線供前線員工查詢。<br />\n<br />\n至於隔離病床方面，公立醫院目前有503張設於負氣壓設施內可即時使用的隔離病床，目前使用率為60%。醫管局會緊密監察使用情況，有需要時可逐步啟用其餘900張設有負氣壓設施的隔離病床。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局會繼續與衞生防護中心保持緊密聯繫，監察最新的發展。"},{"pid":"0b744b525b15c8f886b64bc6f8e06320738f5278","tid":1817961,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:28:17.000Z","msg":"diu"},{"pid":"74947a1b310d740ab540d88f0a74dd744c3b6253","tid":1817961,"uid":108571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"幾日後 香港個案應該會多過武漢"},{"pid":"65d38af4c997e1afc8fec878db853f3c00d81ca8","tid":1817961,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:47:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"150de753790992713e8607c9b8312d732309c697","tid":1817961,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:49:19.000Z","msg":"根本就陰謀黎<br />\n咁就可以止亂"},{"pid":"f70a38453df564b14658ce135ff29dcc55a46988","tid":1817961,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:07:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF07TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=2a1ad3ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"46f64cbf5df3030e8c1f9569fc0e9c81dab2b305","tid":1817961,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:17:27.000Z","msg":"日日10個8個 都唔明邊度咁多人 咁既時勢仲會上去武漢<br />\n都唔知係唔係上面放D病人落去"}]}